SUMMARY:The Fabulous BioTones at the Penngrove Pub
DESCRIPTION:The Fabulous BioTones are fun-loving musicians with serious chops who play rock\, blues\, pop\, and soul. This seasoned\, tight four-piece (with occasional guest stars) plays lively shows of upbeat classics and originals. Come join the party\, and bring your dancing shoes! \nOur Story \nThe Fabulous BioTones hail from the San Francisco bay area\, and are ready to bring their eclectic blend of classics and originals to your party\, benefit or event. \nThey perform upbeat\, high energy and dance-able mix of rock\, blues\, pop and soul. Early influences of the band include many blues and rock figures\, notably Stones\, Beatles and Chess Records – era blues. \nBut wait – there’s more: they also bring a tasty mix of Tom Waits\, Robben Ford\, Ry Cooder\, JJ Cale\, Junior Wells\, and\, of course\, more Beatles. The mix is really fun\, booty shakin’ stuff… \nMeanwhile\, The Fabulous BioTones are currently booking shows and events throughout Northern California for all of 2026. Join the party! We will have us a good time…! \n 
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-fabulous-biotones-at-the-penngrove-pub/
LOCATION:Penngrove Pub\, 10005 Main Street\, Penngrove\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.297140;-122.666400
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Penngrove Pub 10005 Main Street Penngrove CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=10005 Main Street:geo:-122.666400,38.297140
END:VEVENT
