SUMMARY:The Jami Jamison Band at Murphy’s
DESCRIPTION:Jami Jamison and Band\nThe Jami Jamison Band is unique in that they can provide a great evening of entertainment\, get the dance floor full\, or fill the air with soft sounds on a quiet afternoon. Their five piece line up includes an entertaining female lead vocalist\, saxophone\, guitar\, bass guitar and drums. \nTheir music has been described as Jazz\, Blues\, and Swing. \nFrom Billy Holiday\, Etta James\, Peggy Lee\, Louie Jordon to Ruth Brown\, the band seems to satisfy anyone from young to old. \nJami Jamison\, the lead vocalist\, always surrounds herself with seasoned musicians\, guaranteeing quality music. Their combined love of music and each other carries over to audiences\, creating an atmosphere where EVERYONE has a good time.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-jami-jamison-band-at-murphys/
LOCATION:Murphy’s Irish Pub & Restaurant\, 464 1st St E.\, Sonoma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Jami-Jamison-band-S3-1DOppX.jpg
GEO:38.2924023;-122.4558064
